  "specs": {
    "descr": "The Cisco UCS 6652 52-Port Fabric Interconnect is a One-Rack-Unit (1RU) 10/25/40/50/100/400 Gigabit Ethernet, FCoE and Fibre Channel switch offering up to 8.44 Tbps throughput and up to 52 ports. The switch has 32 10/25/50-Gbps Ethernet ports, 4 40/100/400-Gbps Ethernet uplink ports and 16 unified ports that can support 10/25/50-Gbps Ethernet or 16/32/64-Gbps Fibre Channel. All Ethernet ports are capable of supporting FCoE.",
